<br>
If you increase a certain skill 10x you get a 5x stat bonus for that skill type so......<br>
<br>
Say you want Strx5 Endx5 Persx5<br>
<br>
First do your misc skills....<br>
pick a skill with personality trait and train it x10<br>
then pick a skill with str trait and train it x10<br>
<br>
Now train an end minor and major x5 each.<br>
When you level you will get a x5 bonus to an attribute instead of a x3 or 2.<br>
<br>
